<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Latest News</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/normalize/8.0.1/normalize.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: auto;
    }
    .page-title {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .card {
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }
    .card img {
      border-top-left-radius: 10px;
      border-top-right-radius: 10px;
      height: 200px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }
    .card-body {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .card-title {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .card-text {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background-color: #007bff;
      border-color: #007bff;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
      border-color: #0056b3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="page-title">Latest News</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
        <div class="card">
          <img class="card-img-top" src="https://img.nsctotal.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/internacional-x-gremio-1.jpg" alt="News Image 1" >
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Partida de Grêmio X Inter</h5>
            <p class="card-text">Veja a grande partida de grandes rivais.</p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" href="/esportes/futebol">Leia mais</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
        <div class="card">
          <img class="card-img-top" src="https://s2-ge.glbimg.com/IQThuT6cF69peJES22-ouf9B0Eg=/0x0:1080x1350/984x0/smart/filters:strip_icc()/i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_bc8228b6673f488aa253bbcb03c80ec5/internal_photos/bs/2022/y/k/tncBWhSUSQFf0ik7Bbqw/whatsapp-image-2022-07-22-at-18.44.47.jpeg" alt="News Image 2" width="100px">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Contra Shakur Stevenson, Robson Conceição disputará título mundial de boxe no dia 23 de setembro</h5>
            <p class="card-text">Veja a grande partida de grandes rivais.</p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" href="/esportes/boxe">Leia mais</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
        <div class="card">
          <img class="card-img-top" src="https://s2-ge.glbimg.com/4iv1djnQaSfYItdEv9NCrCDCIkE=/0x0:1200x800/984x0/smart/filters:strip_icc()/i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_bc8228b6673f488aa253bbcb03c80ec5/internal_photos/bs/2023/f/M/FjD0JwSEif04oxLxHbHQ/bc4ac1df-b960-afa8-4417-23319c053200.jpg" alt="News Image 3">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Balneário Camboriú recebe última etapa do circuito CBSurf Master na próxima semana</h5>
            <p class="card-text">Veja essa competição incrível.</p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" href="/esportes/surf">Leia mais</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.11.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
